{"tid":1584873,"cid":28,"subCid":0,"title":"熱門暫時只限某幾個台算啦 eg時事台 政事台 站務台","createTime":"2019-09-21T10:39:35.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-29T20:45:52.000Z","uid":152123,"like":21,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"7fe2cf8c38bffa87ecf29cc0f0f0fa67045d496a","tid":1584873,"uid":152123,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-21T10:39:35.000Z","msg":"根本出咩post唔係講新聞就會被人屌死<br />\n就算出個陣冇諗住要上熱門<br />\n永遠有班人衝入嚟屌你on9 post、冇人想知 垃圾post唔好推<br />\n熱門一有其他post就會被屌死"},{"pid":"62a951669c33f7b91bf05de918bc9e5dd4be1589","tid":1584873,"uid":123713,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-21T10:40:12.000Z","msg":"[行動又無人理？] 全球最大親子抗爭活動上線啦！ <strong><strong><span style=\"color: orange;\">#birdfoldingchallenge</span></strong><br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1584614\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1584614</a><br />\n摺一隻紙鳥，影相，放上Facebook / Twitter / Instagram，並加上hashtag #birdfoldingchallenge #929globalmarch #929GlobalAntiTotalitarianism，copy呢段文字再tag 5個朋友，就完成！</strong><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/iYhkXcO.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FiYhkXcO.jpg&h=9b11593e&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"5d46837f551b89a5c451dbd85d80d11e5e840dba","tid":1584873,"uid":47605,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-21T10:50:20.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\">由於都係有好多人唔明行動有咩意義同目標 於是係正式攻略之前出個簡化版</span><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n【行動】【主線】 【922】【SUCK4.0】 【多圖】 【簡易式攻略目標 】<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1583476\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1583476</a>"},{"pid":"4c3a9511db70cd5bb52814a77f372383033e43ef","tid":1584873,"uid":152123,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-21T13:05:04.000Z","msg":"仲有<br />\n正正就係因為熱門會有其他post<br />\n先搞到一大批人用bot洗版 洗曬所有post<br />\n如果熱門只限時政站 就可以順利成章唔畀人用bot"},{"pid":"19c55d7b37ab33667ffd74ffefec652f0e258dd6","tid":1584873,"uid":18265,"like":1,"dislike":3,"score":-2,"